## dmas

**Value type:** `<prop-encoded-array>` encoded as a list of phandle + dma-specifier pairs

A list of phandle and DMA specifier pairs, one pair per DMA channel used by the device. The number of cells in each DMA specifier is determined by the `#dma-cells` property of the referenced DMA controller node.

Used together with `dma-names` to identify each DMA channel by name.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    dmas = <&gpi_dma1 0 7 QCOM_GPI_UART>,
           <&gpi_dma1 1 7 QCOM_GPI_UART>;
    dma-names = "tx", "rx";
};
```
